Text: Downloading it now! Too bad not too many seeders out there! Will let you guys know how good this is once the dl is done! Thanks to who ever uploaded this!

Greetings, I uploaded the file because it could not find it on torrent. Remember to install turn off Internet of your computer and uncheck the option "automatically update" of the installer. See video tutorials on youtube for more examples.

The installation (64 bit) works fine, but when I run the activator I get this error message:

---------------------------
SW2010-2012.Activator.SSQ.exe - Entry Point Not Found
---------------------------
The procedure entry point CoCreateInstance could not be located in the dynamic link library E:_Crack_swactwiz_libFNP.dll.
Never mind my previous comment. It works flawlessly. Thanks!
antianto: how did you get around this error? I keep getting it

Figured it out. Here is a protip if yours doesn't work: replace swactwiz in your setup/i386 folder with the supplied crack (must rename it I found...) and it will work. May give you error messages on startup but still runs! Derp!!
